### 5.8 ASCII UI 原型图 (ASCII Prototypes)（可选）
\`\`\`text
+------------------------------------------+
| $project_name |
|                                          |
| [核心界面元素示意]                        |
|                                          |
+------------------------------------------+
\`\`\`

### 5.9 架构设计蓝图 (Architecture Blueprint - ASCII)

- 技术栈: $tech_stack
- 系统交互:

\`\`\`text
+-----------------+          +-----------------+          +-----------------+
|   Frontend      | -------> |    Backend      | -------> |    Database     |
|   (用户界面)    | <------- |   (API服务)     | <------- |    (数据存储)   |
+-----------------+          +-----------------+          +-----------------+

